*Ostavi≈°* mu knjigu na stolu (You leave him a book on the table).
*Ostavio* sam je pred vratima (I left her at the door).
*Ostavila* je priliku da joj se oprosti (She left an opportunity to be forgiven).
*Ostavljaju* nam samo nade (They leave us only hopes).
*Ostavili* smo znak da se vratimo (We left a sign to come back).